y 27. This crucial event marks the mid-season decider, where the world&apos;s best surfers put it all on the line to advance through the next section of the tour. It is also the third and final stop of the GWM Aussie Treble. Margaret River will bring the action with pumping waves and strong competition." type="episode" contentRating="TV-G" duration="3600000" grandparentArt="https://images.frequency.com/video/7378414391979565541/solid/rectangle/w1920_h1080/15rbv3w2ktoan1ocm8m8691yx5.jpg" grandparentGuid="plex://show/6901610f8c0415b0db4efc88" grandparentKey="/library/metadata/6901610f8c0415b0db4efc88" grandparentRatingKey="6901610f8c0415b0db4efc88" grandparentThumb="https://provider-static.plex.tv/epg/cms/production/8a626fbd-6e1b-48ad-b36a-c634423b9677/2000X3000_WSL_VERT.jpg" grandparentTitle="WSL Inside Pro Surfing" grandparentType="show" index="7" originallyAvailableAt="2025-09-26T18:37:51Z" parentIndex="12" requiresConsent="1" skipParent="1" thumb="https://images.frequency.com/video/7378414129907552616/solid/rectangle/w1920_h1080/c627b8w4fflh123aeytutwzst.jpg" title="Inside Pro Surfing: Western Australia Margaret River Pro 2025" userState="0" year="2025"><Image alt="Inside Pro Surfing: Western Australia Margaret River Pro 2025" type="coverArt" url="https://images.frequency.com/video/7378414391979565541/solid/rectangle/w1920_h1080/15rbv3w2ktoan1ocm8m8691yx5.jpg"/><Image alt="Inside Pro Surfing: Western Australia Margaret River Pro 2025" type="coverPoster" url="https://provider-static.plex.tv/epg/cms/production/8a626fbd-6e1b-48ad-b36a-c634423b9677/2000X3000_WSL_VERT.jpg"/><Image alt="Inside Pro Surfing: Western Australia Margaret River Pro 2025" type="snapshot" url="https://images.frequency.com/video/7378414129907552616/solid/rectangle/w1920_h1080/c627b8w4fflh123aeytutwzst.jpg"/><Genre filter="genre=620143f98578b9238e1cdb8a" id="620143f98578b9238e1cdb8a" key="/library/sections/home/all?genre=620143f98578b9238e1cdb8a" ratingKey="genre_620143f98578b9238e1cdb8a" slug="s